sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as ML Client<br/>(mlflow-skinny)
    participant AppClient as Client Application
    participant OTelApp as Instrumented App<br/>(OTel SDK)
    participant WebUser as Web Browser
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as Auth Module<br/>kubernetes-auth
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic/etc.)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment Run Logging

    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: kubernetes-auth
    MLflow->>Auth: Validate credentials & RBAC
    Auth-->>MLflow: Authorized (workspace-scoped)
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: INSERT run metadata<br/>Auth: Password
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Run ID created

    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-batch<br/>Metrics, Params, Tags
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: INSERT metrics/params/tags<br/>Auth: Password
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: OK

    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Binary artifact data
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Access Keys<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload confirmed
    MLflow-->>Client: Artifact logged

    Note over AppClient,LLM: Flow 2: AI Gateway LLM Proxy

    AppClient->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/gateway/routes/chat<br/>Auth: kubernetes-auth
    MLflow->>Auth: Validate credentials & RBAC
    Auth-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: Retrieve encrypted API key<br/>(KEK/DEK envelope)
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Encrypted secret
    Note over MLflow: Decrypt with AES-256-GCM<br/>PBKDF2-derived KEK
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Decrypted API Key<br/>Encryption: TLS 1.2+
    LLM-->>MLflow: Chat completion response
    MLflow-->>AppClient: Proxied LLM response

    Note over OTelApp,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: OpenTelemetry Trace Ingestion

    OTelApp->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>OTLP protobuf payload<br/>Auth: kubernetes-auth
    MLflow->>Auth: Validate credentials
    Auth-->>MLflow: Authorized
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: INSERT trace spans<br/>Auth: Password
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Traces stored
    MLflow-->>OTelApp: 200 OK

    Note over WebUser,S3: Flow 4: Web UI Browse & Compare

    WebUser->>MLflow: GET / (React SPA)<br/>Auth: kubernetes-auth
    MLflow-->>WebUser: React bundle (module federation)
    WebUser->>MLflow: GET /ajax-api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/search
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: SELECT experiments
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Experiment list
    MLflow-->>WebUser: JSON response
    WebUser->>MLflow: GET /ajax-api/2.0/mlflow/runs/search<br/>Compare runs view
    MLflow->>PostgreSQL: SELECT runs + metrics
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflow: Run data
    MLflow-->>WebUser: Run comparison data
